headline: The Cigna Group Announces Appearance at Barclays 27th Annual Global Healthcare Conference
summary: Global health company The Cigna Group (NYSE:CI) announced today that Brian Evanko, EVP and CFO of The Cigna Group, and President and CEO of Cigna Healthcare, will present at Barclays 27th Annual Global Healthcare Conference on March 12, 2025, through a virtual webcast.

headline: U.S. Managed Care Q4 2024 Earnings Recap: Medical Costs Continue To Mount
summary: US managed care insurers' Q4 2024 earnings season was characterized by generally higher medical costs amid ongoing changes to federally subsidized healthcare plans.
